# LOGO AGENT RULES

## Your task
Create the Bud2 logo as an SVG and wrap it in a reusable React component.

## Files to create
- `src/assets/logo.svg` — the raw SVG (paw print with location pin motif, terracotta #873415)
- `src/components/Logo/Logo.tsx` — the component
- `src/components/Logo/index.ts` — barrel export

## Logo component spec
Props:
- `size`: 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg' (maps to 24px / 40px / 64px)
- `variant`: 'icon' | 'full' (icon only, or icon + "Bud" wordmark beside it)
- `color`: optional override, defaults to #873415

## Where to integrate (check each one)
- `src/components/Navbar` or equivalent top nav
- `src/features/onboarding/` — onboarding header
- `src/pages/Landing/` — hero section
- Any auth screens if present

## Do not
- Use an img tag pointing to a public URL
- Hard-code size in the SVG — use the size prop
- Use any color other than the terracotta primary unless `color` prop is passed